data.description: BACK ON MARKET. Deal fell out of contract, No fault of seller.  Don't miss 2.5% assumable loan.  Must be owner occupied buyer.  Seller is packing up so please excuse the mess.  Backs to open space!! This stunning four-bedroom, three-bathroom home offers an unparalleled living experience that combines modern elegance with the beauty of nature.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the timeless allure of hardwood floors that grace the main level of the home. The open and spacious layout creates a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. To add to the dynamics of this home, you have an office nook on the main level, perfect for home officing. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring sleek countertops, high-end appliances, and ample storage space. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or preparing a meal for your loved ones, this kitchen will make every culinary experience a delight. The family room is a true oasis of relaxation, with its cozy fireplace and large windows that provide breathtaking views of the open space behind the house. Imagine unwinding here after a long day, or gathering with family and friends to enjoy the warmth and comfort of this inviting space. The spacious primary suite offers a private retreat, complete with a luxurious ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family members or guests, ensuring everyone has their ownprivate sanctuary.ASSUMABLE LOAN $443K @ 2.5%. LAKEVIEW HOME SERVICING. FHA Owner Occupied Buyer. Need pre-approval letter from buyer's lender before offer accepted, then to Lakeview for Assumable.
